data.description: One of the standout features of this property is the generous storage space throughout. The additional two-car garage is a definite highlight. This garage not only provides parking for your vehicles but also offers additional space for a workshop or storage for larger items. An extra storage area on the back side of the house offers a bonus space to make sure you have enough room for everything. Inside you'll find two family rooms to increase the livability of the home. The generously sized rooms will give you a comfortable feel. The driveway is accessed from 79th St to make accessibility easier. Welcome home!
